n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ph%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BA%A5m-vi%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-Kim-L%C4%83ng-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%C3%A0i-di%E1%BB%83u-v%E1%BB%8Dng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-qleM3TXt3R77YFpevPeb5w">Thấm viên xuân - Kim Lăng Phụng Hoàng đài diểu vọng kỳ 2 - 沁園春－金陵鳳凰臺眺望其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ph%C3%A1c/author-6WbYdtzdi93NI7sjD0SLkg">Bạch Phác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/Thi%C3%AAn-H%C6%B0ng-tr%E1%BA%A5n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zfk8LWGL0mEgBMai1LRNPA">Thiên Hưng trấn phú - 天興鎮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/author-UlfffDmWp64stOugtjh9rQ">Nguyễn Bá Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Y%C3%AAn-D%C5%A9ng-hu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-To%C3%A1n-b%E1%BB%95-%C4%90an-Ph%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-IVmlKm5t0Hwj5_jveltLGw">Tiễn Yên Dũng huấn đạo Nguyễn Toán bổ Đan Phượng tri huyện - 餞安勇訓導阮算補丹鳳知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o/poem-k1azVfdswKnBXLw7JxxXsg">Triều Tiên quần đảo - 朝鮮群島</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Jg_4_inbL47zGqzn3fJTrw">Lạc Thành Tương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
